─────────────────────────────────────────────
  Cheatsheet
  Alt + /          Cheat sheet (this!)
  Alt + g          Git cheatsheet
  Alt + n          NordVPN menu
─────────────────────────────────────────────
  Terminal Navigation
  Ctrl + a         Move to start of line
  Ctrl + e         Move to end of line
  Alt + b          Move back one word
  Alt + f          Move forward one word
  Ctrl + f         Move forward one character
  Ctrl + b         Move backward one character
─────────────────────────────────────────────
  Editing
  Ctrl + w         Delete word before cursor
  Alt + d          Delete word after cursor
  Ctrl + k         Delete from cursor to end
  Ctrl + u         Delete from cursor to start
  Ctrl + y         Paste (yank) last deleted
  Ctrl + _         Undo
  Ctrl + l         Clear screen
─────────────────────────────────────────────
  Vi mode (normal)
  Esc              Enter normal mode
  i / a            Insert / append
  I / A            Insert at start / end of line
  0 / $            Start / end of line
  w / b / e        Word forward / backward / end
  dd / D           Delete line / to end
  cc / C           Change line / to end
  u                Undo
  k / j            Previous / next history
  / + n / N        Search history, next / prev
─────────────────────────────────────────────
  File system
  Alt + Space      File finder → open in nvim
  Tab              Cycle completions forward
  Shift + Tab      Cycle completions backward
  ls               eza -lh (icons, dirs first)
  lsa              ls -a (show hidden)
  lt               eza tree (level 2, git)
  lta              lt -a (show hidden)
  ff               fzf file finder with preview
  eff              $EDITOR "$(ff)"
  open             Open file/dir in Nautilus
─────────────────────────────────────────────
  History
  Alt + h          History search with confirm
  Ctrl + r         Reverse history search
  Ctrl + p         Previous command
  Ctrl + n         Next command
  Up / Down        History search by prefix
─────────────────────────────────────────────
  Tools
  n                nvim (. if no args)
  t                tmux attach || new -s Work
  c                opencode
  cx               claude (bypass permissions)
  d                docker
  r                rails
  g                git
  gcm              git commit -m
  gcam             git commit -a -m
  gcad             git commit -a --amend
─────────────────────────────────────────────
